Predict the result of these 4 expressions:
The Name Check: guest_name and is_vip
(Hint: If the first value is "True", and returns the second value.)
The Missing Info: invitation_code or "DEFAULT_CODE"
(Hint: If the first value is "False", or returns the second value.)
The Zero Problem: age or 21
(If age is 0, what will this return?)
The Double Not: not not guest_name
(What happens when you flip a non-empty string twice?)

